Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.27,0:00:04.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上一集的Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了突破東京大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:08.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們進行集訓來讓彼此更加團結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:11.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這時 小瑪格麗特竟然在採訪中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:13.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我會告訴大家什麼是真正的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:15.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真正的歌聲究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家互相協助 一起製作歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡自己所能努力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:22.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接受大家的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:24.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,能跟大家一同成長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:26.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們9人找出了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,屬於我們真正的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,東京大賽現在就要公布結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:53.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:00.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:03.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:06.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,全國大賽…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:08.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:10.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們9個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:14.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,贏了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:16.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接下來就是全國大賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:17.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:23.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都在替我們感到開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:30.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於成功超越去年的紀錄了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:34.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,靠我們跟學校全員的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:38.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:40.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不認同這種結果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來 奮戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,掀起我們的旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,爬上巔峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們絕不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要拿下勝利!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:12.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不夠 還不夠 遠遠不夠!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不論何時我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,超越昨天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟能走到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然仍舊不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還是要燃燒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想與你一同歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:29.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想了解尚未知曉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:32.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還會更加成長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不想輕易放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在立刻 Start up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,向頂點前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還要更加 更進一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,更加情緒高昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去實現吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這瞬間 盡自己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:57.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,追尋夢想 盡自己全力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:03:02.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為邂逅 給了我熱情的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:09.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是不可能的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也去實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們會繼續相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯 WE WILL!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小瑪格麗特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:27.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個結果就是大家聽完之後的答案喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學園偶像並非獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為跟大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才能創造美妙的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:35.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是小瑪格麗特無法理解這點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:39.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也不希望妳站上學園偶像的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(#11 夢想)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:59.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我第一次喝到這麼好喝的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看瑪格麗特那樣搞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本來還有點擔心會怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為一年級的都很努力才撐過來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,很可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,網路上也一片好評
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:15.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說今年加入的新成員非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:18.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,芽衣真是愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,接著終於就是全國大會了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:26.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過那個葳恩．瑪格麗特還真是讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:30.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,居然玷汙了神聖的Love Live
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:33.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對她來說 講那種話真是太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,現在她正被猛烈砲轟中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別再參加Love Live了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:42.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明明歌唱得這麼好聽 可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:45.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算不滿 在那種場合講實在不妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然很抱歉 但她是自作自受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼她會那樣說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肯定是因為她很不甘心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只是因為這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,新年…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快樂?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這麼說來今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:10.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,元…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,旦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經跨年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:25.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,半夜果然好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:28.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟北海道比起來不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:30.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過人真的好多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,每年都這麼多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音每年都會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:35.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不太習慣人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在暖桌裡懶洋洋的還比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:41.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在暖桌裡懶洋洋的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳不知道暖桌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:47.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊 其實我家沒有暖桌…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這裡沒什麼人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不用妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:00.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 對當地人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來這裡或許比較能放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:02.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那麼就再次期許
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:08.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望這一年大家能好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:11.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,唱出好聽的歌 舉辦美妙的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,度過一個好年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,度過一個好年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,壓歲錢 我要壓歲錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(Liella! 優勝! 晉級決賽!)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,終於要決賽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(大賽優勝級的問題發言)\N(其他參賽者也議論紛紛)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家還在罵小瑪格麗特…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:39.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是小瑪格麗特的社群
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音樂學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:45.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小瑪格麗特國中畢業之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:49.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好像想去姐姐在維也納就讀的音樂學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我請爸爸翻譯了她社群上的貼文
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上面是這麼寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:02.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可是她為什麼要參加Love Live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這就沒有寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:05.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是為了讓大家刮目相看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過她不是住在維也納嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:14.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只為了這樣就特地跑來日本嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳很在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,知道她考試落榜後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我好像能理解她的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:30.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"明明這麼努力唱歌 為什麼…"的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾妳練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,有什麼事我再聯絡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是現在發的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是小瑪格麗特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是不是認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳沒能進入維也納的音樂學校對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本來想跟姐姐讀同一所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,卻沒能如願對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳從哪裡聽說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳都有寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其實我以前也有考試落榜過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,本來想進音樂班 卻落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別把我跟妳相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們的水準可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 覺得像是被奪走夢想的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,肯定是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:09.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我從小就有個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想讓全世界聽見自己的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:15.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,用自己的歌聲為全世界的人帶來笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我很努力練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,過程也非常開心 一點都不辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:26.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但是 我卻突然無法在他人面前唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對當時的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,音樂班根本是遙不可及的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳是在同情我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,才不是 說什麼同情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,少胡說八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳贏過我 奪走了人家的夢想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,奪走夢想?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這話是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小瑪格麗特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳說我奪走了妳的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:52.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:54.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:57.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這是條件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live在我們那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也算是有點知名度的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果落榜的我能在這裡拿下優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,家人就會考慮幫我推薦插班入學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,插班…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我家是音樂世家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要有家人推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就更有可能進入學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:27.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,或許就有機會跟姐姐們齊名並價了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:30.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以妳才來參加Love Live…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:35.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,否則我根本不會參加這種毫無意義的大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live絕不是毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"妳們在我之上"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:48.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,做出這種評價的舞台跟觀眾都毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳應該也很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:53.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,究竟誰唱得比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:56.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不然妳也可以現在就退賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:10:59.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:04.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,因為我認為是我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還以為妳想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們所有人都是抱著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想將歌聲傳達給大家的想法在唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:15.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,希望大家能合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:21.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這份想法比妳更加強烈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(賀 Liella! 晉級Love Live!決賽!)\N多虧有各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:36.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,(賀 Liella! 晉級Love Live!決賽!)\N我們成功晉級了決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,身為學生會長以及Liella!的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請容我再次向各位致謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真的很謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一鼓作氣拿下優勝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對現在的Liella!來說肯定不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我們集結結丘所有人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為妳們加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,拿下優勝!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,優勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都走到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:00.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我們就努力讓下次也能以笑容收場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:04.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,一年級跟二年級的大家都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可可好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:10.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這一定是小戀媽媽在冥冥之中的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說不定真的是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:17.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓妳們來說 說服力就微妙地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,還在台上欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:27.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳剛剛說微妙是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該說是人品還是什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:35.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要說堇學姐沒什麼人品的話我也同意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,給我等一下 怎麼每個人都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我可不像妳一樣對金錢那麼貪婪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,貪婪是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是具足蟲學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,也有些話是不該說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳聽誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,已經很有名啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:54.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,具足蟲~具足蟲~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快關掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放著不管沒關係嗎 小可可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嗯 看來她好像找到了玩伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,讓我輕鬆不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我才不是玩伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好了 閒聊到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:08.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為了決賽 今天就要開始練習囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,理事長?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:22.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,維也納國立音樂學校?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,無論師資或設備都是最頂級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,可說是世界第一的音樂學校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:34.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小瑪格麗特?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那邊在今天早上寄來一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:45.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"本校想招待結丘女子高級中學的澀谷香音同學"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,"以留學生的身分前來就讀"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:49.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,留學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,詳細資料都在妳手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,時間從今年四月開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學費和生活費的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:59.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,對方說會替妳支付 不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:00.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再來是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我還沒決定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:06.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這當然是妳的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只不過 如果妳今後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真心想走上歌手這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這一定是個絕佳的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.83,0:14:20.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不必現在就給我答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好好思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,聽不見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,四季 裡面沒裝麥克風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我沒預測到會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:32.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音學姐 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:34.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太假了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們剛才在談什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,該不會是背著我們做壞事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:45.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我稍微調查了小瑪格麗特的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:51.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小瑪格麗特?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:56.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她似乎打算進入這所音樂學校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,上面寫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,維也納國立音樂學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是菁英學校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:04.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:08.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,結果理事長就跟我說她有相關資料…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:18.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:22.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都妳知道香音調查了這些事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:30.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我是知道她好像一直很在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在專業的指導下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,畢業生將各自從事希望的音樂工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:45.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,並在第一線持續進行世界性的音樂活動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,夢想?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:59.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我在小時候就已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:09.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好痛 好痛 好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,再舉高一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,找到香音學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:22.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐是真的要去留學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家都在傳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說Love Live結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,學姐就要去維也納留學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家是因為擔心我才來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我不會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:08.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我真的有被邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但我不會去留學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:19.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在進入結丘 成為學園偶像之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:23.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我終於又能說出自己最喜歡唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以我想一直待在這所學校裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續唱更多的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在這三年努力當學園偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:37.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟這所學校的所有人一起變得更加開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,香音同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,其實啊 在東京大賽的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,大家一起分享喜悅的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就心想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:48.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我選擇的這條路一點都沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:52.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,與更多人分享喜悅就是我的目標之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,看來妳的意志很堅定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,意思是學姐會留下來囉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:03.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明年也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,直到畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,都會繼續留下來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們這麼擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那當然囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,要是香音學姐不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:20.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,剩下的學姐就讓人不太能信任了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳說了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:22.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,千砂都同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那個女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:38.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我去買個飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:46.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等一下 我有話要跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:52.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:58.32,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎樣啦 我可沒話要跟妳說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,答案我已經聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:00.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,答案?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就是香音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:05.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,她不去留學 要留在這裡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼會知道留學的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跟妳沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在妳告訴我之前我不會放手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:13.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我今天收到家人的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,如果香音來維也納留學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我也可以一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,說要我在香音身邊學習唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:34.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在小香音身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然因為香音才能回去讓人不悅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但如果這樣就能入學的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:44.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來小香音得到了這麼高的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,被世界第一的音樂學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,話說在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我的想法不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,既然香音不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:00.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我就會靠自己的力量實現夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不會後悔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是的 果然還是沒有很打動我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然我知道這是很難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,做決定的人是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:16.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:34.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,嵐同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:35.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:41.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,把暖桌帶來幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:51.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不是暖桌 是體溫回復機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼看都是暖桌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,原來這就是暖桌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳真的不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:02.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 決賽已經近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,練習練習
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,光看就覺得冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就算是可可也有點嚇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,妳們這樣不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:16.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,只要拿出幹勁 大家一起練習
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:19.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,馬上就會熱起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千 菜單準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:31.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小香音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不 大家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我知道大家一定會反對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,不過 我是真心這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,所以就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:53.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我希望小香音去留學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:55.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,小千…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:13.68,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方 總是能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,名為希望的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:21.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,正在閃爍著 閃爍耀眼光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:24.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,即便跌倒也能再次前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:29.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,在我追逐的夢想前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:34.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,我究竟會走向何處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,場場相遇之中 雖然又會迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,請試著去享受這一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:46.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,覺得「似乎能做到卻做不到」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,最後做到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:51.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,就會很開心 想著要好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:55.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,整顆心都像是要跳了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.35,0:23:00.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,盡情歡笑 放聲高歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:06.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,繼續走向遠方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,世界廣闊無邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:11.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,雖然也有景色會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:14.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,但熱情會始終如一!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:18.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,跨越許多後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:20.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,想實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:24.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,來吧 大家一起去實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.50,0:23:29.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,明天要彈奏出什麼樣的悸動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,去改變未來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:40.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,下集 實現我的故事
